<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.6">
<l>ōtak kaṭali ṉoḷimutti ṉāramum</l>
<l>cātip pavaḷamum cantac carivaḷaiyum</l>
<l>mātakka veṉṟu varuṇaṉ viṭutantāṉ</l>
<l>cōtic cuṭarmuṭiyāy tālēlō cuntarat tōḷaṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Varuṇa sent a necklace of brilliant pearls from the flooded sea,</l>
<l>superior coral, and beautiful bangles</l>
<l>that are befitting [your] greatness.</l>
<l>Crown of effulgent light, tālēlō! You with beautiful shoulders, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
